 Hit e5 long5-hu m7 heng5 i, Khong2-chu2 kong2, Goa2 chiau3 lang5 e5 hoat-tou7 ho2-ho2 ka7 i kong2, i khiok m7 thiaN; che si7 chhin-chhiuN7 eng7 seng-le2 teh khoan2-thai7 ia2-siu3, toaN5 gak8-khi3 hou7 chiau2 thiaN, sng3 si7 goa2 e5 m7 tioh8,m7-si7 i e5 m7 tioh8. Chiu7 kah be2-hu khi3; hit e5 be2-hu chit8-e7 khoaN3-kiN3 choh-chhan5 lang5 chiu7 kong2, Li2 sou2 choh e5 chhan5, tui3 tang-hai2 kau3 sai-hai2, goa2 e5 be2 chhut-lai5, beh tah8-loh8 khi3 chhe7 chiah8, chaiN2-iuN7 oe7 bian2-tit chiah8-tioh8 li2 e5 tiu7-a2 leh? Hit e5 long5-hu thiaN-liau2 toa7 hoaN-hi2, chiu7 chiong be2 thau2 khi2-lai5, hou7 i khan to3-khi3. 
 TaN lun7-kau3 lan2 e5 lang5 teh kau-chiap ong2-lai5, ia7 tioh8 i5-si5 che3-gi5, kian3 ki ji5 chok; na7 chip i chit8 e5 phiah, liah8 si2-pan2 lai5 choe3, tek-khak si7 bo5 li7-ek. Phi2-lun7 tang-thiN beh kau3, chiu7 tioh8 pi7-pan7 mi5-hiu5, he7-thiN tioh8 pi7-pan7 joah8-saN, chhui3-ta tioh8 pi7-pan7 te5 thng, iau tioh8 pi7-pan7 png7; che si7 tiaN7-tioh8 e5 li2-khi3. Thoan5-to7 e5 iu5-goan5 tioh8 an2-ni. Phi2-lun7 na7 kap thou2-thun2 m7-bat seng3-to7 e5 lang5 kong2, tioh8 eng7 khah khoai3 bat khah chhian2-hian7 e5 to7-li2, in chiah thiaN-liau2 oe7 beng5-pek8; na7 tu2-tioh8 khah su-bun5 e5 thak8-chheh-lang5, tioh8 eng7 khah chhim khah o3-biau7 e5 to7-li2, in thiaN-liau2 chiah oe7 jip8 hi7. Siat-su2 na7 kap phok-hak8 su-bun5 e5 lang5, eng7 hit ho7 ha7-teng2 chhou-lou2 e5 oe7 kap i kong2, tu2-tioh8 iong-hu siok8-chu2 hoan2-tng2 long7-khi2 bun5-bek8, an2-ni chiu7 hiah-e5 su-bun5 lang5 thiaN-liau2 hoan2-tng2 oe7 khoaN3-khin, hiah-e5 chhou-kha chhiah-chhiu2 e5, iu7 na2 chhin-chhiuN7 ah-a2 teh thiaN lui5, chu7-jian5 thiaN-liau2 chiu7 boe7 loh8 hi7, iah8 beh thai3 u7 kong-hau7 leh? Kho2-kian3 thoan5-to7 e5 lang5, tioh8 e7 bun5, iah8 tioh8 oe7 bu2, u7 si5 chiau3 lan2 peng5-siong5, u7 si5 tioh8 eng7 bun5-nga2. Sou2-i2 tong-si5 Po2-lo5 teh thoan5-to7, i si7 khoaN3 kau3 sim2-mih8 toe7-hng, tui3 sim2-mih8 ho7 lang5, eng-kai tioh8 kong2 sim2-mih8 oe7, long2 bo5 chip si2 koat. Chhin-chhiuN7 Seng3-keng u7 kong2, M7-thang eng7 chin-chu hiat hou7 ti kau2. Chim-chiok lai5 siuN7 chit e5 i3-su3, thang chai chin-chu u7 chin-chu e5 lou7-eng7, ti kau2 u7 ti kau2 e5 sou2 ai3; beh thai3 oe7 siang7 chit8 khoan2 lai5 gi7-lun7 tit leh? 
 Siu2 tu thai7 thou3 
 Chong-chu2 u7 kong2, Song3-kok u7 chit8 e5 choh-chhan5 lang5, khoaN3-kiN3 chit8 chiah chhiN-kiaN chau2 e5 thou3-a2, chong5-lai5 tong7-tioh8 chhiu7-tu soa3 si2-khi3. Hit e5 choh-chhan5 lang5 chiu7 giau5-gi5 hit chang5 chhiu7-tu, si7 oe7 soah thou3, chiu7 pang3-sak i keng-choh e5 su7, choan-kang lai5 toa3 chhiu7-tu e7 theng3-hau7, ng3-bang7 khoaN3 u7 thou3 oe7 chau2--lai5, thang hou7 lan2 khioh-tioh8. 
 TaN lun7-kau3 thiN-kha-e7 e5 mih8, tak8-hang7 lan2 to u7 hun7, put-ko3 tioh8 eng7 ke3-chiN5 lai5 khi3 boe2, na7 kan-ta khoaN3 teh him-sian7 si7 bo5 lou7-eng7. In-ui7 hian7-si5 e5 lang5 na7 khoaN3-kiN3 koaN-ka chu2-te7, a2-si7 giap8-hou7 kiaN2-sun, tit-tioh8 in si7-toa7-lang5 e5 giap8-san2, kui jit8 chiah8-pa2 eng5-eng5, iah8 bo5 choe3 sim2-mih8 thau5-lou7, kan-ta si3-koe3 thit-tho5 hoaN-hi2 khoai3-lok8, chiu7 kong2, Hit-e5 si7 u7 toa3 sit8-lok8 lai5 chhut-si3, a2-si7 kong2, Thian-chai5 ka-ki7 lai5. Che put-ji5-ko3 si7 kio3 lang5 m7-thang tui3-tiong7 chiN5 gun5 ke3-thau5. M7 ku2 hit ho7 pin5-toaN7 m7 ai3 than3 e5 lang5 siong5-siong5 eng7 che lai5 kong2, ti3-kau3 gou7 lai5 gou7 khi3, ham7-hai7 m7-si7 sio2-khoa2. An2-ni kiam2 bo5 kap chit e5 Siu2-tu thai7-thou3 e5 lang5 siang7 khoan2 e5 gong7 mah? Thai3 m7 siuN7 lang5 oah8 ti7 se3-kan, sui-jian5 thiN bo5 go7 lang5, ia7 tioh8 lan2 pun2-sin chhun-chhiu2 khi3 theh8 lai5 khng3 hit chhui3--nih8. Ho5-hong3 Siong7-te3 siN lan2 u7 kha u7 chhiu2, si7 beh hou7 lan2 un7-tong7 choe3 tai7-chi3, m7-na7 pang-chan7 ka-ki7, ia7 ai3 hou7 pat8 lang5 tit-tioh8 li7-ek. Siok8-gu2 u7 kong2, ThiN-toe7 iN5 lin-lin, chhoan3 go7 si7 toaN-sin. Koh lang5 sng3 si7 ban7-hang7 mih8 te7-it leng5-khiau2 e5, thai3 thang ka-ki7 chau5-that? Chiu7-si7 cheng-siN khim5-siu3 ma7 tioh8 si3-koe3 khi3 tho2 chiah8, boh8-kioh lang5 si7 te7-it hoat8-phoat e5; kiam2 u7 kong2, siN lan2 e5 seng-khu, si7 beh choe3 saN-a2 ke3, pak-tou2 si7 beh choe3 png7-tau2 na7-tiaN7? Sui-jian5 chou2-chiuN7 u7 lau5 tam7-poh8 san2-giap8, kau3-giah8 hou7 lan2 chit8-si3-lang5 thang chiah8, chheng7, eng7, ia7 m7-thang kui-jit8 bu5 sou2 su7-su7. Song3-tiau5 Liok8 Siong7-san u7 chit8 chhiu2 koa, chiu7-si7 choe3 lai5 ka3-si7 chit khoan2 e5 lang5; koa-nih8 kong2: 
 ThiaN, thiaN, thiaN, <BR>Hou7 goa2 tioh8-boa5 thiN chu3-tiaN7, <BR>Na7 beh pin5-toaN7 oe7 iau koaN5, <BR>M7-thang iau koaN5 chiah oan3-mia7, <BR>ThiN-nih8 sin5-beng5 u7 teh thiaN.
 He2-chhiN oe7 sio goan5-ia2 
 Chi-na2 Liat8-kok e5 si5-tai7, Chhou2-kok e5 pian-kai3 Pi-liong5 e5 toe7-hng u7 chit8 e5 cha-bou2 gin2-na2, kap Gou5-kok pian-kai3 e5 cha-bou2 gin2-na2 saN-kap chhai2-sng. Gou5-kok e5 cha-bou2 gin2-na2 in-ui7 kun2-chhio3, gou7 siong-tioh8 Pi-liong5 e5 cha-bou2 gin2-na2. Pi-liong5 e5 lang5 chiu7 chhoa7 hit e5 tioh8-siong e5 cha-bou2 gin2-na2 khi3 chek-pi7 Gou5-kok e5 lang5. Gou5-kok e5 lang5 in-ui7 kong2 oe7 bo5 khiam-sun3, soa3 hou7 Pi-liong5 e5 lang5 ka7 i thai5 khi3. Gou5-kok e5 lang5 au7-lai5 khi3 Pi-liong5 po3-siu5, chiong hit e5 lang5 choan5-ke ka7 i thai5-si2 liau2-liau2. Pi-liong5 e5 toe7-hng koaN thiaN-liau2 chin siu7-khi3 kong2, Gou5-kok e5 lang5 ho2 toa7-taN2, chiah8 goa2 chin kau3, chiu7 nia2 peng khi3 kong-kek i, bo5 lun7 lau7-e5 chiN2-e5 it-chin7 chau5-biat8. 
 Tng hit si5 Gou5-ong5 I5-mui7 thiaN-kiN3 chit e5 tai7-chi3, ia7 toa7 siu7-khi3, chiu7 hoat peng khi3 kong-phah chhou2-kok e5 siaN5-ti5. Tui3 an2-ni Gou5, Chhou2 nng7 kok chiu7 tiaN7-tiaN7 sio-thai5. Gou5-kok chiu7 phai3 Kong-chu2 Kong nia2 peng khi3 cheng Chhou2-kok, ti7 Koe-hu7 e5 toe7-hng toa7 sio-thai5; Chhou2-peng thai5-su, lian5 goan5-soe3 chiong3-koaN, u7-e5 si2, u7-e5 hou7 liah8 khi3. Gou5-peng soa3 khi3 kong-phah Chhou2-kok e5 kiaN-siaN5. Kai-chai3 Chhou2-ong5 chau2 li7, ki5-u5 e5 thou2-toe7 long2 hou7 in chiam3 khi3. Au7-lai5 Chhou2-kok e5 jin5-sin5 jip8 Chin5-kok khi3 chioh peng lai5 khek-hok8 Chhou2-kok e5 toe7. Chhou2-ong5 in-ui7 keng-ke3 chit pai2 e5 thai5-su, chiu7 eng7 sim lai5 pan7 kok e5 cheng3-su7, thiaN3-thang3 i e5 peh-siN3, keng3-tiong7 i e5 jin5-sin5; kau3 kui2 chap8 ni5 au7, Gou5-kok ia7 hou7 Chhou2-kok biat8-khi3. 
 Siok8-gu2 kong2, Sio2-khoa2 m7 pou2, toa7 khang chiu7 kan-khou2. Chit8 liap8 chit8 liap8 e5 he2-chhiN na7 bo5 hoa, oe7 sio pian3 soaN-ia2. Chit8 tih chit8 tih e5 chui2-choaN5 na7 bo5 soah, oe7 piN3-chiaN5 kang-ho5. Bo5 lun7 si7 sio2-khoa2 e5 tai7-chi3, tioh8 siat-hoat hou7 kui tiok8, m7-thang chhut-chai7 i un7-tong7, kau3 chit8-e7 hoat-choh e5 si5, soa3 boe7 siu-sip8 tit. Chhin-chhiuN7 Au-chiu chit nng7 ni5 e5 toa7 kau-chian3, kiam2 m7 si7 tui3 O3-kok Hong5-thai3-chu2 e5 khi2-in mah? Hoe7-iu2 e5 choe3 su7, koh tioh8 chin soe3-ji7, m7-thang liah8 choe3 sio2-khoa2 lai5 bo5 kin2-sin7, kiaN-liau2 oe7 toa7-toa7 chou2-tong3 kau3-hoe7 e5 chin3-pou7. 
 U7 le2-sou3 e5 tit-tioh8 siuN2 
 Chai7-cha2 Liat8-kok e5 si5, Tio7 Siong-chu2 Kap Ti3 Pek put-bok8, bo5 joa7-ku2 soa3 jia2-khi2 kau-chian3. Siong-chu2 tong3 boe7 tiau5, peng pai7 chau2 jip8 Chin3-iong5 siaN5, hou7 Ti3 Pek ui5-khun3 chin ku2. Au7-lai5 khui-tit i e5 chham-bou5 TiuN Beng7-tam5 ho2-taN2 khi3 kiN3 Han5, Gui7, nng7 lang5, soe3 in lai5 poan7 Ti3 Pek, kap Siong-chu2 lian5-hap8, hoan2-tng2 kong-phah Ti3 Pek, kau3 Ti3 Pek biat8 khi3 liau2. Teh siuN2-su3 kong-sin5 e5 si5, khiok si7 Ko Hek tit-tioh8 siong7-teng2 siuN2. Beng7-tam5 siuN7 m7 chhut, chiu7 kong2, Ti7 Chin3-tong5 siaN5 e5 su7, Ko Hek ia7 bo5 toa7 kong-lo5, an3-chaiN2-iuN7 i siuN2 siong7-teng2? Siong-chu2 in3 i kong2, Goa2 ti7 Chin3-iong5 e5 si5, kok-ka chin gui5-hiam2, goa2 e5 ui7 long2 boe7 po2-tit, cheng3 jin5-sin5 e5 tiong-kan, chiu7 tak8 e5 long2 u7 kiau-ngou7 bu2-ban7 goa2 e5 i3-su3, chi2-u7 Ko Hek iu5-goan5 chin khiam-pi, bo5 sit kun-sin5 e5 le2-sou3; sou2-i2 chiah siuN2 i siong7-teng2.
 Hit si5 Khong2-chu2 thiaN-kiN3 chit ho7 oe7, chiu7 kong2, An2-ni chin ho2; Siong-chu2 siuN2 chit8 e5 lang5, chiu7 thiN-kha-e7 choe3 jin5-sin5 e5, long2 m7 kaN2 sit-le2 lah. 
 TaN se3-kan lang5 tai7-khai3 long2 si7 an2-ni; na7 hit e5 lang5 u7 chai5 u7 se3 thang hou7 kho3, lang5 chiu7 pah-poaN lai5 hong7-seng5, chin gau5 phou5-thaN2; iah8 na7 hit e5 lang5 khah sit se3, a2-si7 chiN5 i2-keng liau2, lang5 chiu7 hoan2-tng2 kong2 i e5 si7-hui, leng7-goa7 chit khoan2 e5 bin7-bak8 teh khoan2-thai7 i. Chit khoan2 e5 lang5 siang7 te7-it choe7. Ia5-sou u7 kong2, Lang5 ti7 Siong7-te3 e5 bin7-cheng5, tak8-hang7 tai7-chi3 long2 tioh8 khiam-pi, chiah oe7 tit-tioh8 Siong7-te3 e5 siuN2-su3; na7 kiau-ngou7 chu7-khoa, sui-jian5 u7 kong-lo5, ia7 bo5 tek-khak oe7 tit-tioh8 Siong7-te3 e5 siuN2-su3. Sou2-i2 Hoat-li7-sai3 lang5 e5 ki5-to2, boe7 oe7 siu7-tioh8 hoaN-hi2 chiap-lap8; na7-si7 thiu-hiong3 e5 lang5 teh ki5-to2, hoan2-tng2 tit-tioh8 Siong7-te3 aN3-loh8-lai5 thiaN i. 
 Sui5-ki eng3-pian3 
 Kou2-cha2 u7 chit8 e5 beng2 lang5, kio3 choe3 Pian7 Chong, khoaN3-kiN3 u7 nng7 chiah hou2 kong-ke chiah8 chit8 chiah gu5. Pian7 Chong chiu7 beh khi3 phah hit nng7 chiah hou2; u7 kun toe3 i e5 lang5 kong2, ChhiaN2 ban7 chiah; hou2 sng3 si7 beng2-siu3, gu5 si7 ho2 chiah8 e5 mih8. Hian7-chai7 nng7 chiah hou2, saN-kap chiah8 chit8 chiah gu5, gu5 ki3-jian5 si7 ho2 e5 chiah8-mih8, nng7 chiah hou2 tek-khak oe7 saN-chiN chiah8; na7 saN-chiN chiah8, chiu7 oe7 sio-ka7; iah8 sio-ka7 liau2 toa7 chiah-e5 oe7 tioh8-siong, soe3 chiah-e5 oe7 si2. Li2 theng3-hau7 tiap8-a2-ku2, thai5 chit8 chiah tioh8-siong e5 hou2, kiam2 bo5 it-ku2 liong2-tek mah? An2-ni li2 chiu7 m7-bian2 phah hou2 e5 lo5-khou2, koh-tit-tioh8 thai5-si2 nng7 chiah hou2 e5 ho2 mia5-siaN. Pian7 Chong chiu7 theng3-hau7 bo5 tiap8-a2-ku2, ko2-jian5 nng7 chiah hou2 saN-chiN chiah8 soa3 sio-ka7, soe3 chiah-e5 ka7 kau3 beh-si2 beh-si2, toa7 chiah-e5 ia7 tioh8 tang7 siong. Pian7 Chong chiah oa2 khi3 chiong nng7 chiah long2 tuh8--si2; kng to3-lai5 e5 si5, lang5 m7-chai, chin o-lo2 i, kong2 i chit8 e5 lang5 phah-si2 nng7 chiah hou2, hit e5 mia5-siaN chiu7 chin thau3. 
 TaN bo5 lun7 toh-loh8 chit8 teng2 e5 lang5 teh choe3 tai7-chi3, m7-thang it-bi7 kho3 iong2-beng2, sai2 seng3-te7, ngi7-ngi7 beh choe3; long2 tioh8 sui5-ki eng3-pian3, khoaN3 si5-se3 chiah thang tin2-tang7, chiu7 khah m7 bian2 hui3 siuN choe7 e5 khui3-lat8, koh seng5-kong ia7 toa7. 
 Chin gau5 chhu2 po2 
 Chhou2-kok u7 chit8 e5 lang5, siN3 Pian7 mia5 Ho5, ti7 soaN-nih8 tit-tioh8 chit8 te3 chhou gek8, chiu7 theh8 khi3 hian3 hou7 Chhou2-kok Le7-ong5, ka7 i kong2,lai7 bin7 u7 po2 gek8, Le7-ong5 kio3 tok-gek8 e5 sai-hu7 lai5 khoaN3; hit e5 sai-hu7 kong2, Si7 chit8 te3 chioh8-thau5, thai3 u7 sim2-mih8 ki5-kha2? Le7-ong5 kong2 Pian7 Ho5 si7 khi-phian3 i, chiu7 chiong to3-kha ka7 cham7-khi2-lai5. Au7-lai5 Le7-ong5 si2-khi3, Bu2-ong5 soa3-chiap lai5 che7 ui7. Pian7 Ho5 koh chiong hit te3 chhou-gek8 theh8 khi3 hian3 hou7 Bu2-ong5. Bu2-ong5 iu5-goan5 tiau3 gek8-kang lai5 khoaN3, ia7 kong2 si7 chioh8-thau5. Bu2-ong5 ia7 kong2 i si7 khi kun, chiong chiaN3-kha ia7 ka7 cham7-khi2-lai5. Ke3 bo5 joa7-ku2, Bu2-ong5 ia7 si2, chiu7 oaN7 Bun5-ong5 teh che7 ui7. Chit e5 Pian7 Ho5 chiah chiong hit te3 gek8 theh8 khi3 ti7 soaN-kha, ti7 hia tit8-tit8 khau3, chiok-chiok u7 saN-mi5 saN-jit8, sim7-chi3 bak8-sai2 lau5-liau2, soa3 lau5 huih chhut-lai5. Bun5-ong5 chiu7 kio3 lang5 khi3 mng7 i, Si7 sim2-mih8 ian5-kou3? Kok-lai7 e5 lang5 siu7 cham7-kha e5 heng5-hoat8 si7 chin choe7, li2 siaN2-su7 khau3 kau3 chit khoan2 e5 chham2-chhoeh? Pian7 Ho5 chiah kong2, Goa2 m7 si7 in-ui7 teh khau3 goa2 e5 kha cham7-khi2-lai5, si7 in-ui7 beng5-beng5 si7 po2-gek8, lai5 liah8 choe3 si7 chioh8-thau5, hian7-hian7 si7 lau2-sit8 oe7, ka7 liah8 choe3 kong2 peh8-chhat8; sou2-i2 khau3-liau2 chiah oe7 chiah-nih thong3-sim lah. Ong5 thiaN-kiN3 che oe7, chiu7 phai3 tok-gek8 e5 sai-hu7, lai5 boa5 hit te3 chioh8-thau5, ko2-jian5 lai7-bin7 hian2 chhut po2-gek8, soa3 chiong hit te3 po2-gek8 mia5 kio3 Ho5--si7 e5 phek. Kau3 Chin5 Si2-hong5 e5 si5, Chiong hit te3 phek khek choe3 Hong5-te3 in3; au7-lai5 liu5-thoan5 choe3 kok-po2. 
 TaN Ia5-sou e5 to7-li2, kiam2 m7 si7 bo5 te3 thang chhu2 e5 po2 mah? Ia5-sou u7 kong2, Thian-kok si7 chhin-chhiuN7 khng3 ti7 hng5-nih8 e5 po2-poe3, lang5 khoaN3-kiN3, chiu7 chiong i sou2 u7 e5 khi3 boe7, lai5 boe2 hit te3 hng5. Kho2-sioh lang5 m7 na7 m7-bat si7 po2, hoan2-tng2 eng7 choe7-choe7 hang7 lai5 hui2-pong3. Kau3-hoe7 chhou-siat e5 si5, tu2-tioh8 chin choe7 e5 khun2-tiok8, siu7 chin choe7 e5 leng5-jiok8; m7 na7 chhin-chhiuN7 Pian7 Ho5 hou7 lang5 cham7 kha na7-tiaN7, sim-chi3 u7 e5 pang3-sak siN3-mia7 lai5 kan-cheng3 to7-li2. Kai-chai3 thoan5-to7 e5 lang5 long2 bo5 loe2-chi3, thau5-cheng5-e5 poah8-loh8-khi3, au7-bin7-e5 koh chan7-khi2-lai5. Sou2-i2 chit-tiap8 kau3-hoe7 u7 thang chiah-nih heng-ong7. Siat-su2 lang5 na7 oe7 chhin-chhiuN7 Chhou2 Bun5-ong5 e5 khoan2, chim-chiok lai5 chhui2-mou5, chin ke2 liam5-piN chiu7 beng5-pek8. 
 Sian7 iu2 sian7 po3 
